<HEADLINE> Nasdaq Loses Another 100 Points  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- The Nasdaq Composite Index has lost another 100
points in early trading today. The Nasdaq lost 189.22 to 4,644
yesterday and is down about 8 percent from its record high close of
March 10.
</P>
