   High-tech stocks have sold off for three days straight,
including sharp losses the past two.
</P>
<P>
   The pessimistic mood extended to overseas markets today.
</P>
<P>
   Analysts say the question remains whether investors will simply
cash out of the technology shares, or whether they will put their
profits to work elsewhere in the market.
