   --''The West Wing,'' NBC, John Wells Productions in association
with Warner Bros. Television.
</P>
<P>
   --''American Presidents: Life Portraits,'' C-SPAN, Washington,
D.C.
</P>
<P>
   --Sheila Nevins, Home Box Office, Personal Award
</P>
