<HEADLINE> Eastwood Restaurant To Reopen  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   CARMEL, Calif. (AP) -- Would a Dirty Harry burger make your day?
</P>
<P>
   You may be in luck.
</P>
<P>
   Clint Eastwood's watering hole is reopening. The Hog's Breath
Inn closed last April when one of the actor's partners wanted to
get out of the 27-year-old business.
